            <thead><tr><th>Trigger Class</th><th>Example Observable</th><th>Probability Shift</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><b>Flow restoration</b></td><td>Transit counts recover &gt;70% of the 30-day pre-event mean</td><td>Mass toward A</td></tr>
